  <div class="col-md-12 me-4">
    <p class="text-home">Oolite Developments is a small local building company (based around Woodham) that prides itself on a top-quality finish, with a small team that care, with fair pricing, as we would rather get return business, or recommendation's, rather than a one-off inflated payday.  The company was set up 10 years ago to purchase and develop its own properties, which we did, and now either sold or rented out.  Things have evolved, and we now provide services to the local community, with many projects under our belts. We have a small select team, who are all very approachable friendly and professional . The core of the team is Ashley and I, and we have a small trusted select few subtractors that we work with when necessary (Electrician, plumber, roofer, labourer, waste disposal, landscapers, window/door specialist, carpet fitter)
                        All are projects are initially started with a site visit, where we discuss your vision, and how to make it happen. We specialise in full refurbishments, however we can-do one-off areas of your homes, whether it's a new kitchen, bathroom or anything else you desire.  Landscaping is another forte, and we have done numerous garden projects to date.
                        Projects can be tailored to your budget depending on what your project is, for example, your own home would be a top-quality finish, however if you own a rental, HMO etc, the finish may not need to be the same. We use Building Control on a regular basis, so this can be done by us, or we can provide support to navigate the process.   So, if you have a one bed studio or a detached property, please get in touch</p>

